values:
Hello my fellow people. How are you people doing nowadays? I'm doing fairly well. I mean life is still mediocre. Anyway, I have Eternity's birthday party Sunday. I think we are both getting baptized. Wonderful. There's going to be between twenty and fifty people there o___o; That's a lot. But hey if people love my daughter so much, why not?

On the other hand. My back is constantly killing me. I can't seem to get the pain to go away. I can take Soma. One.. nothing. two... feeling it. But then the pain comes back real quick. It's so fucking annoying. I feel like I'm going to split in two. So therefore I am going to get insurance, and possibly not work. Then I'm going to get a lawyer and file for disabilty. I don't really know if I will be able to get it or not. But you know it's worth a shot if nothing else I will get my back fixed.

Friday I am going to get tubes in baby's ears. Then I'm going to get my permit.. AGAIN. Then I get to go clean the fucking house.I unno. I'm calling Rose State Denistry school to see if they'll clean my teeth and shit so. Yeah anyway, what's up with the world, lemme know.

First off the Linkin Park concert was fucking kick ass. It was so loud it was vibrating my clothes. Chester was sick, and he wanted to cancel the concert because the doctor said he shouldn't play. Then apparently he got really sick supposedly " torn the vocal cords" but he sang at our concert and then said this...

"Hey Everyone in El Paso and Alberqurque ! I wanted to let everyone
know how bummed I am that I am not well enough to play these shows.
I've been sick many times and been able to perform, but this has been
particularly hard on my voice and lungs. I am doing everything I can to
get better ASAP, and will hopefully be back and ready to go for the
Staples Center show. I also would like to thank everyone in Oklahoma
City for being so amazingly awesome during my not so awesome
performance there. I have never felt so much love from a crowd in my
life. I wasn't sure if we were gonna make it through that show, but
the crowd really carried us through it. LP has the best fans in the
world. Thanks for everything..............C"

Labels: chester 

So fucking awesome, what can I say, I will go to another one and have front row seats when he comes back. I swear I will no matter what I have  to do. He was huggin people for Christ's sake. ;_;

We had Wayne's fourtieth birthday today. It was great. I decorated. Got he some presents. A lighter and a magnet that he calls his fuck you presents. Lol. Then I gave him a card that says" I want a fucking cheese burger with some fucking fries and ( I think ) some fucking coffee... (inside)  Happy Fucking Birthday. " It was funny. We've been having sex talks lately because he refused to allow me to wear my school girl outfit to the lp concert. He paid me fifty bucks not to. So I wore all black with black lipstick and call a preppy dude who went to get a :Lp shirt before me I looked at him eye to eye and said COCKSUCKER! He just blinked and looked at Jon then looked away saying nothing n_n.

Sammy's guine pig died and she's cried so much. I feel a lil sorry for her. =/. But alls well thanks for checking. Have a good day.

 

P.S. I just really lied. Big time. My mom has started major shit with me. She claims it is my fault that my dad no longer talks to my sister and is pissed that he came to see me. So she went off on me telling me how horrible I am, that I'm a mooch, and  I don't deserve my kids. So that's the briefing, thanks for listening, later.

<a href="http://www.poetry.com/voteforme/poemvote1.asp?PID=12362462"> Rate my poem, Go here </a> Please vote  a ten for my poem, its being published and I'm one of the top two hundred poets for '07, in Europe and the U.S. So pretty please help me. I could win ten grand >_<!

http://www.myspace.com/me_nuffin_more  <- my normal blog. 

Anyway. Had hell putting Eternity to sleep today. Don't know why, but the little shit doens't want to take naps anymore. PERIOD. >_> Not nice. So while she was asleep I sat there and drew a Superman sign for Wayne while watching LA Ink on DVR. Life's not exactly exciting in this day and time, well at least for me. But no complaints here. I've got a place to live where I'm not being hurt and not having to worry about being homeless, so I'm good. I just need to get my lazy ass up out of this chair and go get a job. Looks like I'm headed to Crest to be a cashier. Oh God how I hate retail. . . six months and I'm already sick of the shit. Walmart drove me insane. But if they think I'm "experianced" Then oh well at least it's a job. Well later, Jon's calling.

Okay! First I had baby in emergancy C-section. Too much epideral, nearly died. Umm. Lived with boyfriend. He sucked bad. Got me in loads of trouble. Almost lived on the street. He started beating me. My mom had to make me leave him. But yeah. Hm But I have a beautiful boy six months old. Brown hair blue eyes a little chunk! He's such a cutie! Fat cheeks and all, looks just like me. I'll have to try and get some pictures on here soon. Well I can't really stay on here much I think my grandfather needs the computer. I'll try to get on here and explain more one day when I go to metro tech again. Oh more BS I had to quit school. I'm telling you I was quite crushed. But anywho Cameo has returned. The real one bigger and badder so get ready!! I'm doing better, having to go through therapy. Heh. Cameo's physco n.n!
-Cameo

Well, I went to the doctor yesterday. With no choice, I am being induced. Dern kid should have been moving more, then I would not have this problem e_e';. So tonight at 6:00 pm CST. I get to start having a baby. Yay... ::yawn:: I am really not ready for this...so tired.... 

This weekand was boring. Really boring. I cannot think of anything I did. Went to the flea market? Yes, that I did. I did not do anything else. Or if I did, I do not recall. How sad indeed. Yanno what..? 

I am hungry. . . 
Food. . . 
Mm. . .
I do not get free food here, no food. ._.'; Man. 

Well, I will speak with you all again as soon as I cna get back. Until a later time~
-Cameo

Yesterday, I found out my sister is, for sure, living with us now. This means, moving my room where my step-brothers' is and sharing it with my sister. Plus, she'll be attending my school as a freshmen. I hate freshmen. When you become a high class-men, you realize how stupid you really were. Lol. I don't mind her moving in at all, because she takes up my moms' time and I don't have to be around all the fucking time. e_e'; Lemme say, that got old. 

When I woke up today. It was cold and windy outside. Cold front moved in, feels pretty good, if you have appropriate cloths for the weather. My legs are hurting like hell though, fun fun. Plus, I ride the bus for an hour and twenty minutes to get a whole mile down the street from my house, if that. 

Plan for today... =/. Am I supposed to have one? 

I have to say thank you to all of you, for being friends, really. I've had completely different responses from other people I've told. That was depressing. Those people I don't really speak with anymore. I gave up trying to keep contact with people who don't give a damn whether I was alive. If I had a computer I guess I would not have had such a problem keeping in touch with you. My apologies, at some point I do intend to get one. By the time I graduate here, I can get at least a part time job making seventeen dollars an hour, I believe I can fit a computer in that budget. Hm, thanks again for the support. 
Much love from a friend, until next time-

First off, how are all of you? Me, I am , uncomfortable but, alive. 

Uncomfortable why? Since many of you have not been told shockingly,yet I appreciate those whom I asked to keep my secret. I am having my first child. He is said to be born next Monday. Yes, I am sixteen. Yes, I plan on getting married to the Father. I can say this has not worked out easily. We are frowned upon. He's twenty-two, I'm sixteen. No, it's not illegal as many believe it to be. I know this,due to the fact, my father tried to have him arrested, it did not work. Colt, my boyfriend, and I have been together not quite a year. Yes, I sound like a whore. Am I? No, not by definition. I've kissed a total of two guys. Only slept with one. No, not a whore. I slept with him four times by the time I got pregnate. Sad sad little girl believing it would not happen to me. Never believe that. It is quite false. I am still living with my mother, because she believes she can have me as a run away if I move out. Also I cannot bare to break my mothers heart. I have not figured out why just yet. 

But this, this is my life. The one I made.. all on my own.

Hello memories of a simple life. Ah the good ol' days, when I could whine and pout. Times change. Hope we all know this by now. Being pushed into the real adulthood. Whoo. Thought I was an adult before. Ha. I wasn't ready. Now not given a choice, actually I was, but I chose this life for myself and it's about to get alot more complicated. Fighting against my mother for the life I've chosen, made the same mistakes she did. Hm, funny I can understand my mothers postition much better now. Next week I'll become an adult, wether I'm ready or not, or wether I like it or not. There's no going back now. . .

Okay, well it is yet again time for me to leave. I will not be on during the summer. Therefore, I shall not have a chance to update my beloved journal. But I wish you all a wonderful summer. Feel free to call me if you wish.If not, that's alright too. Well much love to you all and in my thoughts you'll be.
Farwell For Now,
Cameo (405) 601-7149. Yes, you've been dared to kidnap this child. e_e';

P.S.

  much love to you as well. You were recently added to my friends list. Talk to you over the summer =D.

Very, very bored... I posted my "resume" online. Yoohoo -.-;. I hope people didn't that was hard. Anyway. Hey, tomarrow's my 6 month mark thing with my boyfriend and it's his birthday.Cool in my opinion. nn'; I'm too poor to buy a gift but I can,amazingly, stay till midnight. 

My grades are suffering terribly from mostly the teachers I don't like u.U'; I guess I was absent too much. Get bored with school and don't go...not a good idea, okay...? And Dude I saw this girl come into the class to transfer, but she had the littlest baby i'd ever seen. It was so small. My big ass brothers were nine and ten pounds. But it was cute. ^_^' But ugh yeah grades, suffering because i get side tracked As seen above. 

Nothings new. I'm bored. I guess i shall speak later. Bye

I'm really bored. Computer class is too easy and I type to fast so I get done with work fast. e_e'; Bordem. It hurts. Oh for those of you who didn;t like the fact my boyfriend lived with me: He got kicked out, a long time ago, but still. Now i get to see him maybe once every three weeks. For like five minutes. Yay, isn't life fun?

I've been writing Aaron, only one who TI'm keeping in touch with since I've left the computer. He's pretty cool still, he apologized for being an ass when we broke up. True he was though. Things happen, can't hang on to the bad things in the past, that keeps you afraid and un confident. For instance,my whole problem now is being scared of being "self-centered" Well of coarse you're going to sound self-centered in a journal. It's your journal. Who do you write about in a journal, you and what happens in your life. Coarse, I am different in real life, but, few of you really know that. Guess what? I don't care if you do think I'm self centered anymore. Don't like me? Fuck you, don't talk to me.Manuel..

Sorry I'm in a ranting mood. Thinking about bullshit that's happened lately. With people who I thought were my friends, like Manuel,and then decide because I've changed, and for the better, he's gonna say he doesn't like me. A few things have happened lately that I need to grow up for. I'm not going to stay the same. I suppose one would notice wether or no I have changed if they talked to me. It doesn't appear that I have through this, but oh well. I'm going to leave now. 
Have fun all.

Hi all, 

Sorry if I haven't updated in awhile, got tired of being caught and gripped at. Anyway, I'm alright, stressed which few know why, but happy. I wish i had a computer sometimes, I wouldn't be on Aim half as much as I used to be but it is good to keep in touch, right? Although, it is great to have Word for reports and such, but oh wait! My Father didn't have that. Bleh. *Reminds self...Term Paper Due Monday,NEED TO START IT!!!*

Oh Katt, my girl kitty looks like your kitty only she's a she. Luna's all white and has a pretty face, that's awesome, I like your kitty. ::laughs:: Oh yeah, and Larry works for my Mom now at the airport. She's like oh shit :;grumble grumble grumble:: 

Um, not really much has gone on that I let be known.Feel free to send me e-mails if you wish to keep in touch, I will reply. Till next time. 

Always,
-Cameo

I chickened out I couldn't sing, so I didn't go, i actually stayed home that day. Pitiful huh?

Today in  2nd hour I heard a girl say, " My ribs are showing, so I stopped eating." I mummbled," Your ribs are showing cuz you dont eat enough,jack ass."  The teacher heard me and laughed. ... oops.

Yeah Valentines day was good. I had mine on the sixteenth. We went to pizza hut and ugh got his labret and tongue peirced then went to the mall. Yeah. Fun. I have explained my boyfriend right? 5'9 he's dirty blond...white O.o'; Weird huh and 21. Oh now he lives with my mom and I and he pays her $400.00 a month x.x'; Ah well..

Today is a good day. Happy. Ern I am a sneaky kid, now i have to go before Ms. Sneaky gets caught. Later. 
-Cameo

cool,I'm on a lap top in science heh. This is kinda different. Anyway hi.How are yu all I'm good,happy with bf and mom. Yeah... Itry out for a play/musical tomarrow after school. Please wish me  some luck and hope it travels fast. Um Im in intermediate womens choir. Good ...eh,right? ButIm doing good in school 6 A's 2 B's. Um How are all of you doing?Hm. Btw Valentines day bit ;.;. Oh well. Well talk later,peace!
Cameo

Hi, been really good week. How is Katt? x.x'; I do not see an update and she hasn't commented I do hope she is alright. 

Anyway. I'm in compy class, being really happy,for no reason. Church sucks.. um yeah. Well nm thanks bye

doing pretty good, in exception for the fact I just got told that if you miss for days unexcised you dont get a semester grade. If I do not get a grade, i refuse to come to school for the rest of the year. The end. I'm happy with my bf and we worked things out. Till later
-cameo

I am feeling alot better. I have gained some confidence, Katt was right, I changed. Sadly not for the good. I did only get high once, it bored me. Cutting, well not worth it. I need to get rid of this boy. He is no good. What I really need is friends and people to talk to. My online life was left behind because I needed my mom and she needed me as much. I apologize to all the friends i ahve left behind. I have no one now. But that's okay. I will find more, I just hope you all will still talk to me sometime. It's rare that you do. The only one who comments is Katt. Thanks for caring katt. Your words made alot of sence.

Okay look. i have to say some things in here dont get mad at me. Okay I got high the other night cuz my boyufriend is driving me insane. He told me to stop cutting myself, but he's not around. Instead he has colt watching me, so I smoked pot instead. Not that big of a deal. Seriously, it just made me feel tired that's all. My mom forgot me and I had to walk the mile and a half home. My boyfriend drove  by my house and just waved at me. I was like wth... I started laughing and crying at the same time. Plus, it was Monday. One of the shittiest days of my life. But But the best thing that has been happening to me is the fact Manuel has been calling me. That's the only thing cheering me up. That's wonderful,so glad I've gotten to talk to him. ^v^. Anyway I'm out. 
-Cameo

::Sighs:: Anyway...not having so much fun. I'm depressed again. Back to normal,right, yay Cameo is back. Um. Life's normal, nothings happening in other words, boring.

Hey, I get to dress up as a whore this Halloween. One of these days... Well one of these days I'll get a job and get my own P.C. apparently not soon. Yes, I admit, I am a lazy ass. 

I need to make some phone calls. Need to talk to Allison. Well um school sucks, high school (bleh). Well I am out. Bye

Ugh Rashad my boyfriend came back last night after being gone for a week and a half. I heard one door shut at 11 I knew it was him then two seconds later he was at my house. Happy day. Yeah ugh. Other than that I was depressed. Um spelling test. Making A's out my ass well later.
-Cameo

KAy, I've been doing well, I'm sorry people but  I dont have more than like five minutes on here. So please please post comments about your week =D please? ;.;. I want to read ljs but teacher is like rawrg yanno? Ah well. Week has been so so. Havent spoken to Rashaud my dunno maybe boyfriend who was my first kiss. Yay. That's over with. Now duuno if hes with me. Anyway. Schools fine. All A's sept my D in Geometry. Well gtg later.
Nothing here just starting to get hooked up with neighbor boy. ^_^'; Fun. Anyway. Only new thing. More later, shes talking....AGAIN.

Hey yallz, stills houldnt be on here but w/e. Um I've missed you all so much. Fuck you Sara you could have called me you chose not to. Heh all I can say. Katt hows the NY thing? Is Manuel still alive? xx'; Oh fuck Jeph too asshole. Um. I'm happy =D. Mom rocks.

Gots a dentist appt today, change the color of teh braces. Summer was boring btw, didnt make any friends near me till yesterday. Heh my neighbor Omar myuahaha he hooked me up with two more people to chill with. Kick ass man. Colt and Mike.I thinks Omar thinks I'm hott which is alos kick ass. High school bites people. YOU DIDNT WARN ME XP. Just playin. Its aiight just boring. World History lasts forever man. Anyway. Anybody wanna do my Geometry homework. I'll pay you..ugh eventually. Well.  I gotta go before I get caught. Hope your summers were kick ass. Aiight laters.
-Cameo

hey i am iin computer class gtg before i get caught better update later just wanted to say IM ALIVE! 

Yeah I am back for a few still sneaking heh. Um yeah living with mom is great and im happy. This school is okay, alot of mexicans but the cutest guy is white punky dude >.o me always whining about white boys now look. the shame;Anyway miss you all still getting back to you becca no phone later

Back for a bit. Here to say,I'm living with my mom and probably will rarely be seen for a year, or until I get a job to buy one of these things. Heh. Much better place to live for my poor lil mind. But You can call me at (405)632-8476 for about a month then it will change, if you want to know what it is ask Sara, colatesaddended.

Becca thank you very much for the letter, I promise to send one back with pictures and a drawing mwuahaha. Cha..Oh speaking of pictures. I got my nose peirced, my picture changed. Nyah. Plus I may dye my hair blue... unno yet. But yeah. Hope you are all doing well. I'd die if somthing really bad happened while I was gone. Well,I's okay.See you all some time around Christmas, I', thinking.
Farewell I suppose. Don't think I'll update again before I go.

Have you ever lost somthing dear to you? But at the same time gained somthing good? Has somthing fallen slowly out of your grasp and you can't do anything about it? Has anyone else felt like their whole world fell apart? It's an odd feeling to know that things were taken from you because of one decision. Perhaps what was lost really wasn't lost but merely appeared that way. Maybe it was just your imagination. If it was lost,maybe it will return. There are an endless amount of answers to any question,any choice. Several things in this world that still remain unanswered. After all there is no real answer to anything. It's what people assume is correct,"normal". Just because someone looks like a regular person,doesn't mean they are.From what I've observed, it's the normal people the have had the worst experiances. Then again, I don't know..

Alot of things I say have no meaning,unimportant. Infact, I really don't know if anything that's come out of my mind has been important. I am quite sure none of it was vitial,or necissary. I was told once that if you talked to me for need,you'd already be gone. I'm only for fun right? After all you can't hold a serious conversation with me, can you? 

Hm. Now that I got that out I feel better. I'm not sure of much  anymore. I'm sorry for such a long rant.

I'm sick. I'm shaking and feeling rather ill. I just mowed the lawn. Not a happy camper. 

Special note:
Those who not long desire my friendship tell me, that's all I ask. Yes I do notice those that are trying to get rid of me,I'm not stupid. 

I have four more days left at my dads. Then it's no computer and no phone.I suppose sometime I will send my sister onto AIM to reach the few people that do call me. Damn the distance. e_e'; 

Anyway. Any questions then IM. Bye.

Okay day was and is decent. The end.

The day ended pretty bad. I was supposed to be back on an hour and a half before I was. Then Jeph left. He ignored me in the first place for a more "serious" conversation with Andrea. Sou, heh. I don't know if he called me. May have. But when I come online he tells me goodnight. I'm just like, fine whatever.It appears that since I've been gone people have taken a disliking to me.Like the ones that said they missed me, are the ones who look more like their avoiding me.Perhaps I'm paranoid. But I mean, I understand why Manuel left today. I asked him to. But Jeph just flat out ignoring the "girl he wants to date so much" for his ex girlfriend.. well.. that seems to put a great impression for dating, right? =D.::sighs: Everything exept being Sara's friend again, has been a terrible mess. I really wish I would just give up, don't you?

It's nearing three o'clock. No one is online, still. Sorta sad. Ah well. 

I shall attempt to be online around six. Perhaps to Rp with Jesse and maybe other people. Who knows, all I know is...I need alot of practice. Sara said she knows one who will help me, hopefully he can. Heh.. 

Signed on Gaia yesterday, alot of things have changed, many new places opened up. 

Don't plan on doing much today or tomarrow, try to persuade my parents to let my sister and myself go to the movies tomarrow. Maybe..maybe. 

Not sure if the password on my computer is the same, I'm on Stacie's screen. Doesn't matter I can access everything all the same, just have to go the longer way. 

Wish there were more people to talk to. Talked to Becca this morning. Was enjoyable.Told Sou to go to bed then study ...::sigh:: . Sara and I are talking more. She's grown up a bit. Haven't talked to anyone since Sara.

Hm, Perhaps sometime I'll apply a bit of thought to my entries and make them worth while to read. More about thoughts and beliefs, well..one day.

I've read alot of livejournals. I won't comment. Don't have anything more to say, I'm sorry. Also not much of a conversationalist either. Hm, I've got to find out what I do that upsets people so much. 

Day was okay. I came home and did what I made into a hobby..cleaned. Then I went and saw The Day After Tomarrow. Good movie, but it scares me. 

Now sitting here, I know I shouldn't be online, I mean it's 12:45 and I'm updating livejournal?? Meh merely because I have no one to talk to sept this. Oh well. I'm gonna mess with my web cam now. See if it can come in any more clear...

I have returned. Been pretty lazy I eat and sleep wow O_O IF you have talked to me you know what a THRILLING life it is. Oh yea. I'm here till the fifteenth. Kay. Uh I'm gonna do a better update later. Check ya.,

Alrighty then. I'll be at home for like a whole thirty minutes later. Perhaps I'll get out my cam and take pictures. If my teeth are aching after I return from my orthodonist and Stacie goes to work as plan. ::nods:: 

You guys. I have most of your numbers added to my phone. If you haven't given me your number or I didn't program it >>';; Please IM me on AIM through my phone so I can call.  Because I don't know when I 'll be able to fully use AIM, cuz my phone sucks. So I call. I have Becca,Katt, Manuel, Jeph, Shawn, one from Rafael but ugh... you gave me two different ones... O.o';,going to get Matt's, Chelsey's, Allisons, Sara's, I need Jessica'..maybe you put in my my yearbook..unno, But yeah. 

Last night was not cool. I decided U was going to my moms over dinner. Stacie was being usual Stacie. ee'; Then my phone wasn't working, when it was working people weren't talking. I got pissed and eventually threw my damn phone. At the same time I had been cleaning my room, I cut my finger on a peice of glass and Manuel calls. I got the piss scared out of me cuz I really didn't expect that. But then he got caught callung me but made a deal. I got back on aim apologized a billion times and got Shawn's number. Blah blah. And here I am.

Todays the last day of school... man how come I'm not so excited, I mean I move up to high school next year. Maybe it's because I'll be at Midwest City and not Del City. Anyway~! Talk to you guyses later.

Uh yup. I'm gonna talk to people in boring ol oklie o homa. Over the summer, I'm getting a job. Over the summer I will be at my moms. Hopefully,it will all work out alright. Hopefully. Right? I'll keep in touch with the ones who I've actually had a positive effect on. My sincere apologies to the ones who I haven't. 

Other than that. Very unhappy wiht myself right now. You only get what you deserve after all. Right? 

Banquet Saturday, go with my mother tomarrow. Sunday I'm with my mom. Monday I have some finals. Tuesday I have some finals. Wednesday-? I don't go to school anymore. Yay...right? I guess.

W00t Sou is back Sou is back n___n. Yay. I had a Soda and Junior Mints. Wow. I'm really hyper and stuff.Coffee. Coffee is good. HaHA! Let me see here. I dunno what else to say. sept everyone who reads this, you know I tell everything here because I trust you guys right? Right! Great! Bye!

Got our year books today. My parents bought my sisters year book but no mine. So I went up to the yearbook staff people and had them cancle my sisters and give one to,so yeah. Pissed I didn't get to have it personalized. e_e'; 

Playing neopets. Opened a shop and sold my stuff as soon as I got it in there o_o'; That was scary. But made me happy. 

Lets see I'm updating this thing and waiting to see how much I pissed someone off x_x'; I'm shaking a bit actually. 

Oh, the banquet is Saturday,not Sunday. My plans are all screwed.Be with mom most of the weekand only the rest of this week and two days of school left. But then I start babysitting for two hours every day for a week and earn twenty bucks. Babysit the twerps. 

Well not much left to say. Sept.. where is Sou? =/.
